-Whoo! Psych!

03:39.875 --> 03:43.583
-You're in a good mood.
-Yeah. Why wouldn't I be? Life's good.

03:43.666 --> 03:47.375
What would make life even better
is if you shave the fuzz off that lip.

03:47.458 --> 03:50.500
You gotta be clean-shaven to play
for the Yankees. That's a rule.

03:50.583 --> 03:53.000
Oh, man. That's why I'm a Brewers fan.

03:53.083 --> 03:54.416
I knew I liked you.

03:54.958 --> 03:56.000
Ooh.

03:56.916 --> 03:58.833
-What is this?
-It's a frittata.

03:59.791 --> 04:02.166
-A fri-what?
-A frittata.

04:02.250 --> 04:05.416
I don't know what it is,
but I'm down for anything today.

04:11.500 --> 04:12.666
Mm.

04:14.125 --> 04:15.208
Mm. Mm.

04:16.500 --> 04:18.125
Mm. Mm.

04:18.208 --> 04:22.166
No, don't drown it--
You won't be able to taste the spices.

04:22.250 --> 04:25.000
It's great.
It just needs a little ketchup.

04:25.083 --> 04:26.458
You've done it again.

04:28.041 --> 04:29.041
Mm.

04:36.541 --> 04:39.583
-Can we change the music?
-Driver's choice.

