President Bush
is just doing his best to keep us safe.

04:48.416 --> 04:50.416
Protect us from all those terrorists.

04:50.500 --> 04:52.041
-Yeah, good for him.
-Yeah.

04:54.083 --> 04:57.000
Can we turn down the air please?
It's freezing.

04:57.083 --> 05:00.750
No, we can't.
But next time you can bring a jacket.

05:19.250 --> 05:22.083
Damn. You gonna eat the whole cup?

05:22.166 --> 05:23.916
Maybe. And the stick too.

05:25.250 --> 05:27.708
Oh, shit. It's time for my second round.

05:28.291 --> 05:29.208
Let's get it.

05:31.333 --> 05:33.250
-Hi. Thank you.
-Okay.

05:35.750 --> 05:36.916
Thank you.

05:44.708 --> 05:45.791
Awesome.

05:47.375 --> 05:49.958
Hi. Can I have an ice cream, please?

05:50.041 --> 05:51.916
Sorry, gave you one already.

05:52.000 --> 05:55.250
Oh, but everybody got one already.

05:56.000 --> 05:59.500
I'm not sure about everybody.
I'm sure you did, though.

06:05.208 --> 06:06.250
Hey.

06:07.916 --> 06:11.000
-Where's your ice cream?
-She said I already had one.

06:11.583 --> 06:13.791
What? Everybody already got one.

06:15.208 --> 06:16.875
Hold on, I'll be right back.

06:17.625 --> 06:19.583
No, no, it's cool, I--

06:19.666 --> 06:23.833
No, I'm not getting one for you.
I'm getting my second second.

06:25.833 --> 06:29.541
Like I said, no idea how it worked.

06:35.708 --> 06:37.333
Not yet, anyway.

06:39.208 --> 06:40.041
Thank you.

06:53.333 --> 06:56.458
At least on the field,
I knew what the rules were,

06:56.541 --> 06:59.208
-and I knew what I was doing.
-Let's go, boys. Let's play.

07:03.958 --> 07:05.291
Strike!

07:06.750 --> 07:07.583
Come on!

07:08.166 --> 07:10.875
