-Come on. Come on. You got it.

07:13.833 --> 07:14.875
Let's go, kid!

07:14.958 --> 07:17.083
-Strike!
-You kidding me?

07:18.000 --> 07:20.333
-Come on, ump!
-Good, David.

07:20.416 --> 07:21.875
-Good.
-Good eye, Jake.

07:21.958 --> 07:24.458
Big strike right now!
Big strike right now!

07:25.583 --> 07:28.208
