-Are you serious?

07:28.291 --> 07:29.416
You need to cool off, son.

07:30.125 --> 07:33.791
-Damn it! Kidding me! Come on!
-It's all right. It's all right.

07:33.875 --> 07:36.000
The ump was making some bad calls.

07:36.083 --> 07:38.250
-But Jake's reaction was a bit much.
-Come on!

07:38.333 --> 07:39.583
Let's go, Kaepernick!

07:39.666 --> 07:40.791
Whoo!

07:41.375 --> 07:42.375
I wasn't worried.

07:42.458 --> 07:46.958
All I needed was a halfway decent pitch
to knock one out of the park.

07:47.708 --> 07:48.541
Strike!

07:48.625 --> 07:49.791
-Come on!
-Come on, ump!

07:49.875 --> 07:52.625
-You see? Can you believe it?
-Somebody forgot his glasses.

07:53.208 --> 07:54.750
-Good eye, Colin.
-You got this.

07:54.833 --> 07:56.958
-Colin, hit the ball.
-Colin, Colin.

07:58.041 --> 07:59.208
Strike!

08:00.125 --> 08:03.458
-Open your eyes, ump!
-You got this. You got it!

08:03.541 --> 08:05.208
-Let's go, Kap.
-Come on.

08:05.291 --> 08:08.083
-He ain't got nothing on you.
-Play smart.

08:08.625 --> 08:10.000
-You got this.
-Come on, Colin.

08:10.083 --> 08:11.458
You got this!

08:11.541 --> 08:12.500
Let's go, Colin!

08:15.625 --> 08:16.541
Strike!

08:18.125 --> 08:19.125
Ridiculous.

08:19.625 --> 08:22.708
Hey, watch your tone,
or you'll be sitting in the locker room.

08:23.333 --> 08:28.083
At that moment, I'm wondering
why Jake got a pass, and I got scolded.

08:29.083 --> 08:31.833
Colin's gonna have
to watch that mouth of his.

08:32.875 --> 08:34.291
You're right about that.

08:50.375 --> 08:51.208
Let's do this.

08:52.916 --> 08:54.541
Thursday, a night game.

08:56.666 --> 08:58.250
How's that arm feeling?

08:59.083 --> 08:59.916
Strong.

09:02.750 --> 09:03.833
That mustache.

09:05.083 --> 09:06.041
